            <abstract>
                <p> A miniature showing the Crucifixion of
                    <persName ref="PRS5684JesusCh">Jesus</persName>
                    on the Cross, either
                    dead or alive, or an empty Cross flanked 
                    by two or more figures such as the
                    <persName ref="PRS6819Mary">Virgin Mary</persName> or
                    <persName ref="PRS5695John">John</persName>,
                    the scene typically follows the account of the
                    <title ref="LIT1560Gospel">Gospels</title>, but 
                    may include iconographic elements inspired by
                    apocryphal sources.
                </p>
